I '''Victor-Marie Hugo''' ({{IPA-fr|viktɔʁ maʁi yˈɡo}}) (26 Pebreru 1802 – 22 Mayu 1885) metung yang [[France|French]] [[watas (poet)]], [[playwright]], [[novelista]], [[essay]]ist, [[visual artist]], [[statesman]], [[human rights]] ampong [[activista]] king France. 

King France, ing pangasikat nang Hugo karas keng malagung panyulat menibat mumuna keng kayang kawatasan at kaibat kareng kayang novela ampo karen kayang ikua keng drama. Ding kayang kawatasan ilapin deng ''[[:fr:Les Contemplations|Les Contemplations]]'' ampong ''[[La Légende des siècles]]'' matas la lawe kaya reng criticu at neng misan i Hugo mabibilang yang pekadakila kareng French a watas Kilual ning France, ding kayang bantug a novela ilapin deng ''[[Les Misérables]]'' ampong [[The Hunchback of Notre Dame|''Notre-Dame de Paris'']] (kebaluan keng English bilang ''The Hunchback of Notre Dame''). 


